properties.name: mapDescription
properties.value:
Suitable for up to 200 users.

This map is perfect for a big event in which you want to organize workshop sessions for many people. Enjoy the big lobby with a central Help Desk and the cafeteria for a little break!
So heat up the coffee machine!
